snippet.textDisplay: Oh how the bright burn so fast, that's why I try to stay low lite, like a incense, I smoke up, not burn up the wick. I look in the mirror I see blue, I see me, I see you,  I'm just flying on my nimbus,   smoking my herb, wish more saw this Earth, and not the human curse. This sad whirlpool of confusing dispair, how crazy this paraxdox has become, they record for fun, for a vid, for  a clip worth more then a feeling of being in another's shoes, how far n close it's brought us for the wrong reasons, how many eyes is the new money, how many views, how many likes, that's there life, ain't that funny, thats death living only asking for a value of time or ur life, Did y'all forget you got a random destruction of time n order, never know what that universe the judge will order.-Cm
